#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:1
msgid "E4032"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `type_not_found`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`type_not_found`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:5
msgid "The type is undefined."
msgstr "这个类型未定义。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:7
msgid ""
"This error happens when a type annotation, constructor path, trait bound,"
" or other type position refers to a type that is not in scope."
msgstr "当类型标注、构造器路径、trait 约束或其他类型位置引用了当前作用域中不可见的类型时，会出现此错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:12
msgid ""
"pub fn make(x : Missing) -> Unit {\n"
"  //          ^~~~~~~\n"
"  // Error: The type Missing is undefined.\n"
"  ignore(x)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:18
msgid ""
"Use a type that is defined and visible from the current package, or "
"import the package that defines the type."
msgstr "使用当前包中已定义且可见的类型，或导入定义该类型的包。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4032.md:21
msgid ""
"pub fn make(x : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(x)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
